 một ngày nọ, huấn luyện viên Amakusa của anh ấy đã đề nghị anh ấy giải nghệ. Cô con gái Rei đã động viên Shoutarou đang đau khổ, thế nhưng đã có một cuộc chạm trán đã khiến số phận của gia đình Aragaki thay đổi.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"107408","season":1,"vote_average":6.2,"vote_count":19},"modified":"2025-06-23T14:53:19.000Z","cast":["Daisuke Namikawa","Rina Honnizumi","Kensho Ono","Kenyu Horiuchi","Kaji Yuki","Atsuko Tanaka","Kappei Yamaguchi"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Daisuke Namikawa","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Daisuke Namikawa","tmdb_id":110665,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iw0X8oDutxaBAri3Ifga8nhdUJK.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/110665"},{"name":"Rina Honnizumi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Rina Honnizumi","tmdb_id":2285491,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5p8wWjqrBHTkOPC5txO1eUXRBRY.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2285491"},{"name":"Kensho Ono","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kensho Ono","tmdb_id":1065297,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wUYJ3HIeygHfh4rAqupE4RPoG3W.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1065297"},{"name":"Kenyu Horiuchi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kenyu Horiuchi","tmdb_id":1222060,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qIsrjSbtdhmmUdd3xvpDHNWRuJp.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1222060"},{"name":"Kaji Yuki","name_vi":"Kaji Yuki","name_original":"Yuki Kaji","tmdb_id":149894,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8wKdPV11IwowfwoqGqMMNt9hmp6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/149894"},{"name":"Atsuko Tanaka","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Atsuko Tanaka","tmdb_id":34923,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pacuup8TMK9SFsSJOY8jlbyzkFt.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/34923"},{"name":"Kappei Yamaguchi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kappei Yamaguchi","tmdb_id":68472,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mJyxKRZxLv9D7LH5KcNSkjSKYOB.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.